      "title": "Railway fares increased",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Railway fares will be increased with effect from midnight on Friday (22), said Sri Lanka Railways",
        "According to a gazette notification, the minimum fare has been increased from Rs.10/- to 20/-."
      ],
